ai.skymind.pipelines.executioner

Class PipelineExecutioner

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.skymind.pipelines.executioner.PipelineExecutioner

  • public class PipelineExecutioner
extends Object
    A handler for parsing binary input and then depending on the model loader and model type, (provided by sub classes) the handler will perform inference and send the binary result back down to the user.
    Author:
    Adam Gibson
